{"tid":1136992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【資料庫】迪基亞衰過卡利奧斯","createTime":"2019-05-03T11:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T17:18:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8365051d1822ddb3a03c7374b99f4b3d23833289","tid":1136992,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T11:55:31.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】貴為近年英超最佳門將之一，迪基亞今季表現慘不忍睹，數據上比起前利物浦門將卡利奧斯更差！蘇斯克查剛表示會續委以重任，或多或少是膽博膽。<br />\n<br />\n迪基亞（David de Gea）對上4場出現3個失誤導致失球，數字相當於過往123場的總和，可見近況差勁，今季表現與之前比判若兩人，甚至比現時借到比錫達斯的卡利奧斯（Loris Karius）更不堪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://根據WhoScored.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9AWhoScored.com&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjKcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=6e91b575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">根據WhoScored.com</a>數據顯示，迪基亞在今季聯賽失了53球，平均分只有6.46分，場均失1.4球。卡利奧斯失了39球，場均失1.2球，表現平均分有6.7分。迪基亞今季未救過12碼，傳球成功率僅58.8%，相反，卡利奧斯曾救出一記12碼，傳球成功率也有60.1%。<br />\n<br />\n「無人可以為了失分而痛斥他，曼聯不是他而排名第6位。」儘管迪基亞似乎信心盡失，又或心不在焉，但仍獲紅魔主帥蘇斯克查力撐到底，蘇B表明下周日對哈特斯菲爾德，續由迪基亞正選把關。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"ece8690406b7d4e1cbdd0e2f7e07b61bc62b4edc","tid":1136992,"uid":16659,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/0e65dfba6072b41de00c5ed8cfd414eb/tumblr_pq2jztCGcL1w50dq4o1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F0e65dfba6072b41de00c5ed8cfd414eb%2Ftumblr_pq2jztCGcL1w50dq4o1_500.gif&h=f62bfe42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd4a6f6060b4af5fb0774dbf025160e731e5880","tid":1136992,"uid":13275,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"最衰拉莫斯，撞親卡利奧斯再導致我地ddg表現失準"},{"pid":"c948a51874407e5f0d388bb0fb91357150309625","tid":1136992,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20